                    <br><br>If your business is going through a period of change and you're uncertain about what
                        infrastructure to take on board&mdash;particularly from a technology point of view&mdash;<b>I can't recommend Rapid enough</b>.</p>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Second Testimony -->
                <div class="flex-item-testimony">
                    <div class="testimony-speaker">
                    <div class="testimonial-head">
                        <img src="/images/testimonials/Darryl-H.png">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="testimonial-name">Darryl Hopkins</span><br>
                        <span class="testimonial-company"><b>Torsion Homes</b></span>
                    </div>
                    </div>
